Simple demo programs showcasing `retrofire` features.


============================== Demo binaries =================================

  * `bezier`:  A Bézier curve bouncing around, like in a 90s era screensaver.
  * `crates`:  A scene demonstrating a first-person camera and WASD controls.
  * `hello`:   A bouncing message, pass a custom message on the command line.
  * `solids`:  A collection of different solid shapes, hit space to switch.
  * `sprites`: A ball filled with a large number of spherical particles.
  * `square`:  A minimal-ish example rendering a textured, transformed quad.

